			"text": "所以这个时候也需要和业务共同去复盘一下"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:07,560",
				"to": "00:05:10,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 307560,
				"to": 310560
			},
			"text": "看看到底是运营层面的问题"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:10,560",
				"to": "00:05:13,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 310560,
				"to": 313560
			},
			"text": "还是说业务技能方面的问题"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:13,560",
				"to": "00:05:17,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 313560,
				"to": 317560
			},
			"text": "第三个阶段就是寻盘量与质量订单的均衡"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:17,560",
				"to": "00:05:22,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 317560,
				"to": 322560
			},
			"text": "那么在这个阶段我们寻盘的质量是有所提升了"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:22,560",
				"to": "00:05:25,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 322560,
				"to": 325560
			},
			"text": "提升了之后我们还要继续干嘛呢"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:25,560",
				"to": "00:05:28,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 325560,
				"to": 328560
			},
			"text": "就继续去提升寻盘量"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:28,560",
				"to": "00:05:29,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 328560,
				"to": 329560
			},
			"text": "因为质量有了"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:29,560",
				"to": "00:05:33,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 329560,
				"to": 333560
			},
			"text": "我们就想办法去提升有质量的寻盘的数量"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:33,560",
				"to": "00:05:37,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 333560,
				"to": 337560
			},
			"text": "时刻关注这些寻盘的质量和评估"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:37,560",
				"to": "00:05:39,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 337560,
				"to": 339560
			},
			"text": "如果你在操作的过程中"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:39,560",
				"to": "00:05:42,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 339560,
				"to": 342560
			},
			"text": "发现寻盘的质量又有所下降了"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:42,560",
				"to": "00:05:44,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 342560,
				"to": 344560
			},
			"text": "那么你就要开始去调整了"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:44,560",
				"to": "00:05:49,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 344560,
				"to": 349560
			},
			"text": "因为你不能为了追求这个数量的急剧增长"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:49,560",
				"to": "00:05:52,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 349560,
				"to": 352560
			},
			"text": "然后寻盘的质量回到了第一个阶段"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:52,560",
				"to": "00:05:54,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 352560,
				"to": 354560
			},
			"text": "那么这样的话也是不合理的"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:54,560",
				"to": "00:05:57,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 354560,
				"to": 357560
			},
			"text": "所以说一定要时刻的评估寻盘的质量"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:05:57,560",
				"to": "00:06:01,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 357560,
				"to": 361560
			},
			"text": "第三个就是要与业务持续的合作"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:01,560",
				"to": "00:06:03,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 361560,
				"to": 363560
			},
			"text": "提升订单的转化"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:03,560",
				"to": "00:06:07,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 363560,
				"to": 367560
			},
			"text": "也就是平时我们知道的哪些产品效果非常好"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:07,560",
				"to": "00:06:09,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 367560,
				"to": 369560
			},
			"text": "而且发来的寻盘质量非常高"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:09,560",
				"to": "00:06:15,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 369560,
				"to": 375560
			},
			"text": "那么针对这些产品我们一定要告诉业务积极的去用信保订单去绑定"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:15,560",
				"to": "00:06:22,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 375560,
				"to": 382560
			},
			"text": "同时呢我们要向业务获取一些当下客户需求的一些趋势"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:22,560",
				"to": "00:06:28,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 382560,
				"to": 388560
			},
			"text": "比如说现在客户对哪个品类哪种类型的产品更喜欢"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:28,560",
				"to": "00:06:32,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 388560,
				"to": 392560
			},
			"text": "那么这种问题最好的就是能跟业务沟通一下"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:32,560",
				"to": "00:06:34,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 392560,
				"to": 394560
			},
			"text": "看看能不能给你提供一些信息"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:34,560",
				"to": "00:06:39,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 394560,
				"to": 399560
			},
			"text": "这样就有利于你在后期在操作店铺的时候更加有侧重点"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:39,560",
				"to": "00:06:43,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 399560,
				"to": 403560
			},
			"text": "所以我们整体上来说还是要跟业务共同合作"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:43,560",
				"to": "00:06:45,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 403560,
				"to": 405560
			},
			"text": "一起去打造这个店铺的"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:45,560",
				"to": "00:06:47,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 405560,
				"to": 407560
			},
			"text": "单独靠运营的话"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:47,560",
				"to": "00:06:49,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 407560,
				"to": 409560
			},
			"text": "那么这个效果就没那么明显"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:49,560",
				"to": "00:06:54,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 409560,
				"to": 414560
			},
			"text": "那么以上就是关于新店铺发展的三个阶段"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:54,560",
				"to": "00:06:56,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 414560,
				"to": 416560
			},
			"text": "大概要三到六个月"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:56,560",
				"to": "00:06:59,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 416560,
				"to": 419560
			},
			"text": "如果你按照这个阶段去发展的话"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:06:59,560",
				"to": "00:07:02,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 419560,
				"to": 422560
			},
			"text": "基本是每个阶段都需要两个月"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:02,560",
				"to": "00:07:05,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 422560,
				"to": 425560
			},
			"text": "因为这是国际上是批发类的平台"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:05,560",
				"to": "00:07:08,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 425560,
				"to": 428560
			},
			"text": "它不可能马上这么快速的见效"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:08,560",
				"to": "00:07:10,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 428560,
				"to": 430560
			},
			"text": "除非你的产品很好"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:10,560",
				"to": "00:07:12,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 430560,
				"to": 432560
			},
			"text": "以及你的资源很多"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:12,560",
				"to": "00:07:15,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 432560,
				"to": 435560
			},
			"text": "不然的话你都需要时间去积累"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:15,560",
				"to": "00:07:17,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 435560,
				"to": 437560
			},
			"text": "所以我们在做新店铺的时候"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:17,560",
				"to": "00:07:20,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 437560,
				"to": 440560
			},
			"text": "一定要先构思你要怎么样去做这个店铺"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:20,560",
				"to": "00:07:23,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 440560,
				"to": 443560
			},
			"text": "你的整体的流程是怎么样的"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:23,560",
				"to": "00:07:25,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 443560,
				"to": 445560
			},
			"text": "时间节点是怎么样的"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:25,560",
				"to": "00:07:27,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 445560,
				"to": 447560
			},
			"text": "那么有了这个时间轴"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:27,560",
				"to": "00:07:31,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 447560,
				"to": 451560
			},
			"text": "你所要去做的事情就非常明确"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:31,560",
				"to": "00:07:34,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 451560,
				"to": 454560
			},
			"text": "以及你想要看到的效果"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:34,560",
				"to": "00:07:37,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 454560,
				"to": 457560
			},
			"text": "在哪个阶段会有什么样的结果"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:37,560",
				"to": "00:07:39,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 457560,
				"to": 459560
			},
			"text": "你都有一个清晰的一个预估"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:39,560",
				"to": "00:07:41,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 459560,
				"to": 461560
			},
			"text": "这样你去做事情就比较有条理"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:41,560",
				"to": "00:07:44,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 461560,
				"to": 464560
			},
			"text": "而且你能够非常的知道"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:44,560",
				"to": "00:07:46,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 464560,
				"to": 466560
			},
			"text": "你每周每个月要做什么"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:46,560",
				"to": "00:07:49,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 466560,
				"to": 469560
			},
			"text": "这样就不至于你浪费很多的时间"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:49,560",
				"to": "00:07:51,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 469560,
				"to": 471560
			},
			"text": "就能够在尽可能短的时间内"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:51,560",
				"to": "00:07:53,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 471560,
				"to": 473560
			},
			"text": "把这个店铺做起来"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:53,560",
				"to": "00:07:55,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 473560,
				"to": 475560
			},
			"text": "这个就是关于新店铺"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:55,560",
				"to": "00:07:57,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 475560,
				"to": 477560
			},
			"text": "或者是接受新店铺时候"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:57,560",
				"to": "00:07:59,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 477560,
				"to": 479560
			},
			"text": "所用的一些思路跟方法"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:07:59,560",
				"to": "00:08:01,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 479560,
				"to": 481560
			},
			"text": "希望这些思路跟方法"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:08:01,560",
				"to": "00:08:03,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 481560,
				"to": 483560
			},
			"text": "能够帮助你真正的"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:08:03,560",
				"to": "00:08:06,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 483560,
				"to": 486560
			},
			"text": "把一个新店铺快速做起来"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:08:06,560",
				"to": "00:08:08,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 486560,
				"to": 488560
			},
			"text": "这节课我们就先讲到这里"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:08:08,560",
				"to": "00:08:10,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 488560,
				"to": 490560
			},
			"text": "下节课我们再见"
		}
	]
}
